channel.title: Won't Let Me Back In?
channel.description:
New problem. :D I found out how to do servers, was testing pickup codes, pnpc codes, I type in the infinity top code and it logs me off, logs me back in, and logs me off again. It won't let me back in now. :/
Please tell me what to do? I have the thingy for coding and stuff [not good at coding, lol] but I need back in to get a good server so I can actually have some players on. :[ Help?

item.title: Won't Let Me Back In?
item.dc:creator: @Scarecrows Scarecrows
item.description:
@Scarecrows wrote:

For your new problem, the source you downloaded might have had a ban trigger for those commands, in your config folder which can be found in the source you downloaded look for the file bans.txt or ipbans.txt and see if your name is in there, if so delete it. Also redesign the ban trigger so that it will not ban you for that command. Also this board is for moparscape client questions, should post this in the development and help section.
